Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveThe country home  of the President-General of Ohanaeze Ndigbo Worldwide, Prof George Obiozor at Awo- Omamma, Oru East Local Government Area of Imo,  has been bombed.
It was gathered that the suspects, aka unknown gunmen, used Improvised Explosives Devices, IED and petrol bombs destroy building.
According to eyewitnesses, the gunmen drove into the compound about 6:15am, Saturday, shot indiscriminately for over 15 minutes before setting the building aflame.
Micheal Abattam, the Imo State Police Public Relations Officer, PPRO, confirmed the attack, adding no report of lives lost.
